name: RBC Quant U.S. Dividend Leaders ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to provide unitholders with exposure to the performance of a diversified portfolio of high quality U.S. equity securities that are expected to provide regular income from dividends and that have the potential for long term capital growth. Portfolio securities for the RBC Quant U.S. Dividend Leaders ETF will be selected and weighted using a rules based, multi factor investment approach that considers a company's balance sheet strength, the stability and sustainability of its dividend payout and/or its ability to pay or grow dividends in the future. The portfolio holdings will be reconstituted and rebalanced initially on a quarterly basis. The frequency of the reconstitution and rebalancing may change without notice.
